directory_title="Media RSS Feed Slideshow. Slideshow from Picasa."
description="Media RSS Feed Slideshow. Slideshow with title of Feed and title of pictures. Can display the original picture. Can define display and transition time. Display jpg, gif and png pictures. Random order available."
